    "By integrating visual and linguistic information, these approaches enable robots to understand and execute complex tasks with greater accuracy and flexibility.",
    "The fusion of multiple modalities allows for a richer and more comprehensive understanding of the environment, facilitating more robust decisionmaking processes.",
    "For example, Shao et al. (2021) presented a new imitation learning framework combining natural language instructions and visual inputs for enhanced robot manipulation, offering improved generalisation, efficient learning, and handling of complex manipulations.",
